\noindent{\bf Exploiting Language Models:}
Pre-trained LMs can be leveraged 
to i) encode item-user signals into transformer-based embeddings, ii) infer recommended items from rich representations of review texts, or iii) implicitly incorporate the latent ``world knowledge'' of the LM.